text:
Texas Longhorns 4-Star DE Commit Taquon Graham Cancels Oklahoma Official Visit Taylor Estes 9:15 AM Four-star defensive end Taquon Graham has changed his weekend official visit plans. 
2017 Texas Longhorns commit Taquon Graham had plans to travel to Norman, Okla. for a weekend official visit with the Oklahoma Sooners . 
That plan is no more. 
HornsDigest.com and our friends at SoonersIllustrated.com have confirmed the latest on the defensive end's decision to not officially visit Oklahoma.
